{
  "stem": "1860.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "After being such a successful businessman in Europe, he was working here as a-- a cafeteria cashier on  the night shift.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So his means were limited.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But nevertheless, he took a few weeks off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he saved up some money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was going with us from department stores to department stores and buying things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were just bewildered with-- with all the goodies that were here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I visualized life in America, you know, in-- in-- in comfort and great luxury.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess, to me, America and Hollywood was all the same.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We lived in uptown Manhattan in New York on Audobon Avenue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a small apartment, but everything was-- we were thrilled with everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It didn't really-- it was a modest, small apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that was in 1946.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, we-- we came-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] A few-- two weeks after we came, I started working.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I just-- I knew that everybody in America has to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And besides, being through-- going through concentration camps, I was not afraid.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I would do just almost anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And while I lived in-- in Rotterdam, I was taking history of art.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I did study some painting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I came to the States, I had to-- I felt I have to earn a living, even though my father was against it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was painting on silk, fabrics, wood, metal, all kind of novelties.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's how-- I was thrilled with my first earned money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't know-- First of all, I bought gifts for my parents, and then I-- my father couldn't get over it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He used to say, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You have always time to spend it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You just-- [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
